    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. The power delivery is linear and aggressive, managed by six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that ensures a broad torque curve up to its 8,000 RPM redline. This unit is equipped with the tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal power distribution. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis is further enhanced with upgraded bushings and adjustable dampers, sharpening turn-in response and managing unsprung weight effectively. While the aesthetic reflects a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical vitals are synchronized for peak performance, offering a visceral, analog experience.",
